  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/800e8ed7a6730e6dd79ce81163865ec5.avif?t=1748162351\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/a9329d1102f21ac691539d55a52c99b5.avif?t=1748162351\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>Welcome to our thrilling 2D platformer game! Prepare for an immersive adventure in a captivating world filled with excitement and mysteries to uncover.<br>Explore mesmerizing landscapes, from enchanting caves to dark worlds, as you embark on a hero's journey. Your goal is to navigate through challenging levels, avoiding cunning traps and evil enemies along the way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/ab49db44353389ab8d30f9f5311da313.poster.avif?t=1748162351\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/ab49db44353389ab8d30f9f5311da313.webm?t=1748162351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/ab49db44353389ab8d30f9f5311da313.mp4?t=1748162351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/7bdaa48744ae453e5bf22d1751e32c94.avif?t=1748162351\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>● Use 'A' to move left and 'D' to move right, guiding your character through the mesmerizing landscapes.<br>● Press 'S' to activate the slow-motion ability, enabling you to react swiftly to tricky obstacles.<br>● Tap the 'Space' key to jump, and for an extra boost, double-tap 'Space' to perform a spectacular double jump.<br>● When speed is crucial, press 'Shift' to dash through obstacles and enemies with lightning speed.<br>● Illuminate your path by pressing 'Q' to activate your trusty flashlight, unveiling hidden secrets in the darkness.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/b365059f25048b0032e75c633fc6d204.poster.avif?t=1748162351\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/b365059f25048b0032e75c633fc6d204.webm?t=1748162351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/b365059f25048b0032e75c633fc6d204.mp4?t=1748162351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As you progress, you'll encounter fascinating characters and unravel an engaging storyline, making your journey all the more rewarding.<br>Experience a smooth and seamless gaming adventure with our easy-to-master controls, designed to keep you fully immersed in the action. Are you ready to embark on this thrilling 2D platformer adventure and become a true hero? Let the journey begin!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/4fe38c42536924509eb3439a56acf7e3.poster.avif?t=1748162351\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/4fe38c42536924509eb3439a56acf7e3.webm?t=1748162351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/4fe38c42536924509eb3439a56acf7e3.mp4?t=1748162351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But that's not all, deep within the skies, hidden within a mystical cave, lies an ominous and fearsome evil boss. Its presence casts an eerie aura, unsettling players to their core. With each step, the ground trembles, and the air grows colder. The players brace themselves for a harrowing encounter, knowing only true bravery can overcome this celestial challenge.<br>But Beware... Do not ever Awaken the Boss...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/a308c7a6a0ea1bd2d03d5cb236a4ba73.poster.avif?t=1748162351\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/a308c7a6a0ea1bd2d03d5cb236a4ba73.webm?t=1748162351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/a308c7a6a0ea1bd2d03d5cb236a4ba73.mp4?t=1748162351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/800e8ed7a6730e6dd79ce81163865ec5.avif?t=1748162351\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/a9329d1102f21ac691539d55a52c99b5.avif?t=1748162351\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>Welcome to our thrilling 2D platformer game! Prepare for an immersive adventure in a captivating world filled with excitement and mysteries to uncover.<br>Explore mesmerizing landscapes, from enchanting caves to dark worlds, as you embark on a hero's journey. Your goal is to navigate through challenging levels, avoiding cunning traps and evil enemies along the way.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/ab49db44353389ab8d30f9f5311da313.poster.avif?t=1748162351\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/ab49db44353389ab8d30f9f5311da313.webm?t=1748162351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/ab49db44353389ab8d30f9f5311da313.mp4?t=1748162351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/7bdaa48744ae453e5bf22d1751e32c94.avif?t=1748162351\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><br>● Use 'A' to move left and 'D' to move right, guiding your character through the mesmerizing landscapes.<br>● Press 'S' to activate the slow-motion ability, enabling you to react swiftly to tricky obstacles.<br>● Tap the 'Space' key to jump, and for an extra boost, double-tap 'Space' to perform a spectacular double jump.<br>● When speed is crucial, press 'Shift' to dash through obstacles and enemies with lightning speed.<br>● Illuminate your path by pressing 'Q' to activate your trusty flashlight, unveiling hidden secrets in the darkness.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/b365059f25048b0032e75c633fc6d204.poster.avif?t=1748162351\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/b365059f25048b0032e75c633fc6d204.webm?t=1748162351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/b365059f25048b0032e75c633fc6d204.mp4?t=1748162351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>As you progress, you'll encounter fascinating characters and unravel an engaging storyline, making your journey all the more rewarding.<br>Experience a smooth and seamless gaming adventure with our easy-to-master controls, designed to keep you fully immersed in the action. Are you ready to embark on this thrilling 2D platformer adventure and become a true hero? Let the journey begin!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/4fe38c42536924509eb3439a56acf7e3.poster.avif?t=1748162351\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/4fe38c42536924509eb3439a56acf7e3.webm?t=1748162351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/4fe38c42536924509eb3439a56acf7e3.mp4?t=1748162351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But that's not all, deep within the skies, hidden within a mystical cave, lies an ominous and fearsome evil boss. Its presence casts an eerie aura, unsettling players to their core. With each step, the ground trembles, and the air grows colder. The players brace themselves for a harrowing encounter, knowing only true bravery can overcome this celestial challenge.<br>But Beware... Do not ever Awaken the Boss...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/a308c7a6a0ea1bd2d03d5cb236a4ba73.poster.avif?t=1748162351\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/a308c7a6a0ea1bd2d03d5cb236a4ba73.webm?t=1748162351\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2537330/extras/a308c7a6a0ea1bd2d03d5cb236a4ba73.mp4?t=1748162351\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
